metadata.description:
As we recognized on our last trip, the multiverse space-time transporter isn't perfect yet. Not only does my hair color change, but I think there is a problem with the scaling function. Maybe I've grown too big, everything is small! Surprised, I found a hole that was perfect for me and hid myself.

Phew... but what is that running towards me over there?
metadata.name: TRAIN TUNNEL #1/30
